msgid ""
"The `gmtime()` function returns a date-time tuple in UTC, and "
"`localtime()` returns a date-time tuple in local time."
msgstr "`gmtime()` 函数返回 UTC 中的日期时间元组，`localtime()` 返「回本地时间中的日期时间元组。"

